title: War of the Roses: A Threesome Gone Wrong?
description: Jason convinced his girlfriend, Kim, to have a threesome with one of his friends.  They did it once and it went well so they did it for a second time.  What happened the second time now has Jason questioning if Kim is now hooking up with his friend.
